x4freetext: twelve 180 microm thick Si crystals, backed by two 3
mm and two 8 mm thick Ge crystals.
The raw data were stored event by event
on magnetic tape. The detected particles were sorted
according to their mass and charge, and two-
dimensional matrices were generated of particle`s
energy vs associated m-fold coincidences. The angular
distributions the relative normalization was done
through the number of counts in the monitor telescope
